'''Hamilton Camp''' ([[October 30]], [[1930s#1934|1934]] &ndash; [[October 2]], [[2005]]) provided the voices for [[Rune Haako/Legends|Rune Haako]] and the [[TIE/sa bomber/Legends|TIE Bomber]] [[TIE pilot|pilot]] in ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]''.

He was involved in another [[LucasArts]] game, [[Wikipedia: Full Throttle (1995 video game)|''Full Throttle'']] released in 1995.

